messages.message: Hey all, just a reminder that the December code cut is this coming Monday Dec 7. @Aaron Tami will be the coordinator this month (thank you!!). Updates can be found on the <#CGQ7BD72A|> channel. ~It’s likely this release won’t actually go to any customer, but mostly a checkpoint for our code before the holiday season.~
This release will actually be pushed to GS :slightly_smiling_face:

@shaunak @Heymian we will try out end to end QA automation for this release as well! We have automated considerable number of test in the flow land.. this will be more of a validation run to compare with the manual UAT.. if everything is good we can formally kick off the process from Jan release.. let me know if you want to look at the demo sometime.. @Ramesh is ready with the first set of automation!!
oh that would be awesome, would definitely like to see what automation framework we have in place! and if we can integrate that on a more regular basis?
Cool! Let me setup sometime to go through this! This is just a start, but we can get there soon!! :slightly_smiling_face:
